  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378540/extras/336108be633953ce4ef1282d434918ed.webp?t=1727864911\" width=600 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A catastrophic event has knocked you out during the first day on the job… you wake up equipped with a heavy-grade exoskeleton, in a destroyed section of the complex. Robots gone haywire, insane augmented co-workers and rogue AI - everything wants you dead. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defy deadly enemies and huge bosses in tight, visceral melee combat. Target and slice specific limbs off your foes, with a next-gen loot system where you loot what you dismember. Equip, upgrade and craft new weapons and armors sliced from enemies, and make yourself stronger through a fresh take on leveling-up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378540/extras/8e06b05ab8c9be0bd477f771bdc7321a.avif?t=1727864911\" width=590 height=315 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378540/extras/336108be633953ce4ef1282d434918ed.webp?t=1727864911\" width=600 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A catastrophic event has knocked you out during the first day on the job… you wake up equipped with a heavy-grade exoskeleton, in a destroyed section of the complex. Robots gone haywire, insane augmented co-workers and rogue AI - everything wants you dead. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defy deadly enemies and huge bosses in tight, visceral melee combat. Target and slice specific limbs off your foes, with a next-gen loot system where you loot what you dismember. Equip, upgrade and craft new weapons and armors sliced from enemies, and make yourself stronger through a fresh take on leveling-up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378540/extras/8e06b05ab8c9be0bd477f771bdc7321a.avif?t=1727864911\" width=590 height=315 /></span></p>",
